_sText: THIS IS MY FIRST PREFAB I've made 2 types of crates and they're broken down like this. Plain - 3 different color schemes - each color scheme has 3 different sizes (64x64, 48x48, 32x32) Plain (Rounded) - 3 different color schemes - each color scheme has 3 different sizes (64x64, 48x48, 32x32) Bars - 3 different color schemes - each color scheme has 3 different sizes (64x64, 48x48, 32x32) Bars (Rounded) - 3 different color schemes - each color scheme has 3 different sizes (64x64, 48x48, 32x32) All the crates are individually grouped so just click anywhere on the crate and it selects the whole thing. In other words... There is 36 crates in this pack. DON'T FORGET TO ADD ME TO YOUR WATCHLIST!
